50|$|<b>The</b> University of <b>Houston</b> <b>Police</b> Department (UHPD) is {{the campus}} police for <b>the</b> University of <b>Houston.</b> <b>The</b> {{officers}} of UHPD are peace {{officers of the}} State of Texas whose primary jurisdiction is any county in which <b>the</b> University of <b>Houston</b> owns, leases, rents, or controls property. Their authority {{is derived from the}} Texas Education Code Sec. 51.203 which allows <b>the</b> University of <b>Houston</b> System Board of Regents to employ and commission peace officers. <b>The</b> University of <b>Houston</b> <b>Police</b> Department serves as a division of <b>the</b> University of <b>Houston</b> Department of Public Safety (UHDPS). Its headquarters are at 4051 Wheeler Street (changed from 3869 Wheeler Street in July 2015 in a campus address reorganization) at the southwest corner of <b>the</b> University of <b>Houston</b> campus in <b>the</b> Stadium District.|$|R
